data.description:
Discover the epitome of rural living in this exceptional 4-bedroom, 2-bath home nestled on a sprawling 6.2-acre oasis. Just moments away from the renowned World Equestrian Center, this property combines convenience and charm in perfect harmony.
Upon entering through the fully fenced front gate, you'll be welcomed into a realm of possibilities that cater to both luxury and functionality. The property's prime location ensures easy access to the equestrian world's heart, making it a haven for horse enthusiasts and professionals alike.
Envision a lifestyle where your passion for animals and nature thrives. With fully fenced paddocks and thoughtfully designed feed sheds boasting cover on both sides, your equine companions will revel in comfort and care. Horses, cows, ducks, goats, and chickens coexist harmoniously on this diverse landscape, creating a captivating tapestry of rural life.
Step inside the fully renovated home, where modern elegance meets rustic allure. Meticulously updated, this residence offers seamless integration of contemporary comforts and classic character. With 4 bedrooms to accommodate your family's needs and 2 tastefully appointed bathrooms, every detail has been considered to enhance your living experience.
Outside, the property's charm is elevated by the presence of majestic, mature oak trees that generously dapple the land with shade. Whether you're engaging in outdoor pursuits, relishing in serene moments, or hosting gatherings, the natural canopy creates a picturesque setting that's both calming and enchanting.
This property is more than just a home; it's a sanctuary where your dreams unfold. With easy access to the world-renowned equestrian center, your passion for horses can truly flourish. The fully fenced front gate ensures your privacy and security, allowing you to relish in the beauty of your surroundings without a care in the world.
Seize this rare opportunity to own a move-in-ready haven amidst the splendor of nature, where modern luxury meets rural charm. Embrace a lifestyle of serenity, beauty, and equestrian excellence - all just a stone's throw away from the World Equestrian Center. Your new chapter begins here, where every moment is enriched by the harmony of home and nature.
